Package: work.tkgstrator.kioukifexporter
Name: KiouKifExporter
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: KIOU (Shogi) kifu auto-export tweak. Watches every match in KIOU and, the moment a game ends, calls the app's built-in KIF writer (GameController.GetKifuText) and saves the result as a .kif file under the app's Documents/KiouKifExporter directory so it shows up in the Files app for AirDrop or hand-off to a kifu viewer (PiyoShogi, Shogi Browser Q, etc). No HTTP server, no WebSocket, no host-side bridge — strictly iPhone-local. Observation-only with respect to game state. For authorized testing only.
Maintainer: NEVER KNOWS BEST
Author: tkgstrator
Section: Tweaks
Depends: mobilesubstrate
